{"tid":1753561,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［即時行動］今日光復理大！","createTime":"2019-11-25T03:24:34.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-25T04:00:10.000Z","uid":154039,"like":7,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"c5dc6347afc90a53d634e49436d27e083881097b","tid":1753561,"uid":154039,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T03:24:34.000Z","msg":"今日區選大勝，<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>即刻入理大救人</strong></span>，唔好食人血饅頭。呼籲所有勝出區選之人，一同前往理大，乘勝追擊。（你唔撚係贏區選就滿足啊嘛？）<br />\n<br />\n建議時間：1700<br />\n地點：尖沙咀<br />\n行動：聚人，步行往理大，和理非。<br />\n<br />\n沙盤推演：<br />\n1）武力清場。新聞畫面愈暴力，經民意授權&amp; 全世界關注的區議員，就愈能帶起國際輿論。具體將區選跟「反送中」、「自由民主」扣連。大勝。<br />\n2）拉据。獲得國際輿論，沒損失，小勝。<br />\n3）光復理大。不解釋。<br />\n<br />\n準備：做好英文標語牌，自己帶在身，文具則自行決定。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">和理非係出場，就今日。</span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"7250eb2e745308a3649c5d0475b65060ea29d52e","tid":1753561,"uid":154039,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T03:24:45.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c3cf561196904b9abc13463b8c809bc2f8d83c7e","tid":1753561,"uid":154039,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T03:24:55.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"1a845f358da95fa55105a08251a3877f1206353e","tid":1753561,"uid":154039,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T03:25:05.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"cc19b162494b00c4014417b400029957062ada0d","tid":1753561,"uid":154039,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T03:25:15.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"7ed828bf942cc57150f8cf0ad1308b66e8fc94e8","tid":1753561,"uid":154039,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T03:25:27.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"62fa6ab7094789ab57528d8f1dffe02137a42bff","tid":1753561,"uid":229494,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T03:25:34.000Z","msg":"怕唔怕100%DQ"},{"pid":"26ca6f5c4c2f13361132601ef06e56152082d65a","tid":1753561,"uid":154039,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":